{"type":"text","timestamp":1775894233947,"sessionID":"ses_2847648f1ffemm5w2whyZmaXXZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8b4907001B0CkDDuBy7PcKI","messageID":"msg_d7b8b1812001IjkNXcwDXe2HVZ","sessionID":"ses_2847648f1ffemm5w2whyZmaXXZ","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-023 archive, here is the summary:\n\n---\n\n## AR-023 Archive Summary: CLI invoke/status 命令\n\n### ✅ Completed\n\n**Core Implementation (100% Complete):**\n- **`InvokeRuntime`** (`agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`) — Full implementation with:\n  - Agent invocation via AgentCube provider (AgentRuntime CR)\n  - Direct HTTP invocation via Kubernetes provider\n  - Session header injection (`X-Agentcube-Session-Id`)\n  - JSON payload validation and header parsing\n  \n- **`StatusRuntime`** (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`) — Full implementation with:\n  - Status retrieval from AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR)\n  - Status retrieval from Kubernetes (Deployment/Service)\n  - Rich table output with color-coded status\n  - Proper exit codes for automation\n\n- **CLI Commands** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`):\n  - `invoke` command with `--workspace`, `--payload`, `--header`, `--provider`, `--verbose` options\n  - `status` command with `--workspace`, `--provider`, `--verbose` options\n  - JSON payload validation and error handling\n  - Header parsing with `key:value` format support\n\n- **Service Provider Extensions:**\n  - `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime()` method for CR queries\n  - `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status()` for Deployment status\n  - All prerequisite validation logic\n\n- **Package Infrastructure:**\n  - Console script entry point (`kubectl-agentcube`)\n  - All dependencies specified in `pyproject.toml`\n  - Proper module exports in `__init__.py` files\n  - All 5 runtime classes (Pack, Build, Publish, Invoke, Status)\n\n**Verification Status:** ✅ COMPLIANT — The implementation meets all specification requirements as verified in `VERIFICATION_REPORT_AR023.md`.\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ Deferred\n\n**Unit Tests (Not Implemented):**\n- `tests/unit/test_invoke_runtime.py` — Missing\n- `tests/unit/test_status_runtime.py` — Missing  \n- `tests/unit/test_cli_invoke.py` — Missing\n- `tests/unit/test_cli_status.py` — Missing\n\n**Integration Tests (Not Implemented):**\n- `tests/integration/test_invoke.py` — Missing\n- `tests/integration/test_status.py` — Missing\n\n**Example Agents (Directories Empty):**\n- `examples/hello-agent/main.py` — Directory exists, file missing\n- `examples/math-agent/main.py` — Directory exists, file missing\n\n**Note:** Per the verification report, tests and examples were \"not required for spec compliance\" and marked as low priority.\n\n---\n\n### Summary Statistics\n\n| Category | Planned | Completed | Deferred |\n|----------|---------|-----------|----------|\n| Runtime Classes | 2 (Invoke, Status) | 2 | 0 |\n| CLI Commands | 2 (invoke, status) | 2 | 0 |\n| Unit Test Files | 4 | 0 | 4 |\n| Integration Tests | 2 | 0 | 2 |\n| Example Agents | 2 | 0 | 2 |\n\n**Overall Completion:** Core functionality 100% complete, testing/examples deferred to future sprint.","time":{"start":1775894233944,"end":1775894233944}}}
